title: 1.11.2无法召唤实体
author: Yusai
txt_content: 我在弄地图的时候发现1.11.2无法召唤实体，指令是：/summon VillagerGolem ~ ~1 ~ {CustomName:"铁傀儡",CustomNameVisible:1,PersistenceRequired:1,Attributes:[{Name:generic.attackDamage,Base:10},{Name:generic.maxHealth,Base:200}]}帮忙看看是怎么回事,谢谢!
